flowchart LR
    classDef stage fill:#eaf3ff,stroke:#5b9bd5,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef anchor fill:#0b5cab,stroke:#0b3a6b,color:#ffffff,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef control fill:#eef7ee,stroke:#6aa84f,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef evidence fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#9aa0a6,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.2px;

    Design[Design asset\nclass + terms + permissions]:::anchor --> Onboard[Onboard participants\nidentity + claims]:::stage
    Onboard --> Issue[Issue / distribute\ncontrolled launch]:::stage
    Issue --> Transfer[Transfer / settle\nex-ante checks stay active]:::stage
    Transfer --> Service[Service asset\ndistributions • corporate actions • redemptions]:::stage
    Service --> Close[Close out / redeem\nfinal ownership state]:::stage

    Registry[Unified registry\nownership + compliance state]:::control
    Audit[Audit trail + monitoring\nactivity, evidence, exceptions]:::evidence

    Design --> Registry
    Onboard --> Registry
    Issue --> Registry
    Transfer --> Registry
    Service --> Registry
    Close --> Registry

    Registry --> Audit
    Audit --> Design

    Note[DALP stays involved after issuance; servicing and redemption remain part of the same governed lifecycle.]:::evidence
    Note -.-> Service
